text.text: Had a decent americano surrounded by cats,  what's not to love?  I discovered this place by accident when exploring SLC since I am from out of town.  Great place for those looking to adopt and find the right one in a low pressure environment or just wanting to chill with a coffee or play with some cats!

Clean, well lit cafe area with tables and benches to enjoy a cup of coffee and a delicious cookie next to a quiet, enclosed space with soft and friendly kitties! There are also games and activities to enjoy while you visit and are all cat-themed! The staff here are so friendly and accommodating. Some of the cats are also available for adoption! I definitely recommend this place for cat lovers!!!

Cat cafes are always nice to go to. But this one is extra special as the cats are from a local shelter and up for adoption. What an absolutely wonderful idea.
As a bonus. The coffee was nice as well!
